{"tid":1715114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實香港警察咁多年黎係市民眼中都一直係狗","createTime":"2019-11-13T04:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:01:09.000Z","uid":227275,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ccec84d9c2c9787dc66c899a3bce4e36380ea967","tid":1715114,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:15:53.000Z","msg":"就算未有雨傘運動 香港有部份人都係叫警察做狗 其實依家睇返以前啲電影都會見到<br />\n<br />\n就算係2014年打後 <br />\n普通市民都係當佢地係狗 <br />\n以前成日都會係Facebook見到市民拍片屌d藍衫行咇狗 佢地跟本聲都唔敢出 <br />\n根本窮人又屌得 有錢人又屌得<br />\n中產以上果d更加唔當佢地係人 <br />\n<br />\n依家? 就算你渣波子都捉你出黎打<br />\n大肚婆都打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全係唔撚同晒 <br />\n就係因為你班到依家都唔出聲既港豬 中立撚<br />\n遊行唔敢出唔緊要 捐錢好撚難咩<br />\n我見到身邊d偽黃只係識係ig屌 <br />\n一蚊都唔撚捐 <br />\n一人捐一千都可以好撚多<br />\n你地平時食餐飯都唔止喇仆街<br />\n利申 覺得搞d乜9捐錢challenge會有用<br />\n之前捐錢比water bucket challenge都咁撚多人玩 依家國難當前都冇人捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有d藍絲以為自己好撚把閉有人照?<br />\n差佬同你有親咩on9 出起事上黎藍絲第一個幫警狗做肉盾 時間問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1ea9c222334ddc4fa996f7ef84037501ae6fdd","tid":1715114,"uid":337761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T04:18:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">連登冷氣軍師 rt like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你哋已經唔使上前線搏命，係咪連呢啲都做唔到？</span><br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaVtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=0d94b824\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655